data.description: Discover the allure behind this unassuming exterior.  Interior unveils a blend of luxury and practicality  Vaulted Ceilings throughout create architectural interest and a feeling of spaciousness.  The chefs eat in the kitchen seamlessly connecting the family room, forming the heart of the home.  French doors lead to a covered patio, hot tub and pool area.  Practical laundry room and a well-placed half bath.  Concerned about energy costs? Embrace sustainability with impact windows and a Tesla-powered solar system, ensuring not only efficiency but also minimal power bills.  Adding to the appeal is a small, easy-to-manage yard, providing outdoor enjoyment without the burden of extensive maintenance.  Seize the chance to make this house your home!
